  "reference_number": "GAC0056",
  "remarks": "\nLada FIRTASH is an involved person within the meaning of the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis of the following grounds: (1) FIRTASH is or has been involved in profiting financially or obtaining any other benefit from serious corruption. Specifically, FIRTASH has profited financially from the corruption of her husband, Dmitry FIRTASH; and (2) FIRTASH is associated with a person who is or has been involved in serious corruption, namely her husband Dmitry FIRTASH. \n",
